WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.500
The arm starts above the workspace with the blue, yellow, and red cubes visible.

00:00:02.500 --> 00:00:05.500
It moves toward the cube area with the gripper open.

00:00:05.500 --> 00:00:08.500
The gripper passes over the center cube and continues toward the red cube.

00:00:08.500 --> 00:00:11.500
It aligns with the red cube instead of selecting the intended blue cube.

00:00:11.500 --> 00:00:14.500
The gripper closes on the red cube and lifts it from the table.

00:00:14.500 --> 00:00:17.500
The arm carries the red cube away from the pickup area.

00:00:17.500 --> 00:00:21.000
It lowers the red cube near the target area.

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:23.667
The arm releases and withdraws, showing the incorrect red pick.
